imdb.plot outline: The Hustle is Real Documentary Series concentrates on the philosophy and strength behind the various types of hustles in New York City and their characters. From street sales and nightlife hustlers to lifestyle and corporate hustles each concentrating on the success after the struggle and hard work. With a goal to motivate and inspire others that would have had rather given up, The Hustle is Real gives you a taste of beautiful minds and personalities that have overcome challenges to reach their goals and turn surviving into thriving. Based in the concrete jungle of New York City, Anna Naumi gives you a taste of New Yorkers' lives through her lens.
